long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Create new Documents for Google Drive from your browser bar.

Add a simple menu to your browser bar to quickly create new Documents, Spreadsheets, Presentations, Forms, keep and Drawings for Google Drive.
